node.text: Mark the date! Friday 18th Feb. @lisadtaddeo the bestselling, award winning author of the ground-breaking Three Women and Animal is my second guest on the @service95 podcast. It’s a fascinating discussion, that covers feminism, female desire, Lisa’s upcoming show and her insider tips on West Village, New York. You won’t want to miss it. So, don’t. Out on Friday and available to listen wherever you get your podcasts or via the link in my bio 🤍

node.text: I’ve had the great pleasure of talking to my first podcast guest for @service95 - creative director of Balmain @olivier_rousteing about breaking boundaries in fashion, searching for his roots, his favourite Parisian day-off activities, and more. Subscribe now wherever you get your podcasts before Friday’s premiere to hear it as soon as it’s out 🌐✉️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by DUA LIPA on June 23, 2022 tagging @service95. May be an image of text that says 'ISSUE SUE021 021 OUTNOW OUT NOW SERVICE95'.

node.text: Can you believe we’re entering our sixth month of @service95 with Issue 021? If you haven’t subscribed yet, be sure to visit the link in our bio to get this week’s newsletter for free, which features my ode to natural wines, as well as a gripping feature on @zarasnapp’s quest to legalise drugs in Mexico, a look at the increasingly popular dream therapy and much more. We’d love to know which issue has been your favourite so far?
